{c_label}Cooldown: {/c}{c_resource}{Cooldown Time}{/c} seconds
Raheir strikes the ground {c_number}3{/c} times, each burst dealing {if:SF_6}{c_number}{payload:STARTER}{/c}{else}light{/if} Physical damage and Pulling In enemies. The final burst {if:SF_6}deals {c_number}{payload:FINISHER_BONUS_TOOLTIP}{/c} more Physical damage{else}deals additional light Physical damage{/if} and additionally Stuns enemies for {c_number}[{SF_5}]{/c} |4second;seconds.
